scopes.name: schedule_only
scopes.explanation: Lines 7-220 contain the full text of the ISDA Schedule to the Master Agreement, including all the negotiated terms, parties, and signatures. The content before line 7 is cover/title, and after line 220 is the Confirmation and not part of the Schedule. The Schedule typically ends with the execution/signature blocks, which are at lines 207-220. This span excludes the standard pre-print, CSA annexes, and the swap confirmation that follows.
